calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Eoneren</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Executive Summary</h2> <p> During the quarter, the Lazard Emerging Markets Equity Advantage Portfolio underperformed the MSCI Emerging Markets Index (net of fees). Stock selection and sector allocation both detracted. Stock selection was strongest in materials and communication services. Health care and information technology holdings</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1922505318/image_1922505318.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745596-lazard-emerging-markets-equity-advantage-portfolio-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 17:25:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745591", "title": "Party On", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Presidential Election Betting\" data-id=\"2181544373\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Douglas Rissing</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Things are not as dismal as some think. The reaction to the Fed\u2019s announcement of their last cut and the expectations that surrounded it whacked the market on Wednesday as if the future had dimmed significantly. There was probably</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2181544373/image_2181544373.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745591-party-on", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 17:20:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745572", "title": "Novo Nordisk Stock: A Rare Buying Opportunity", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/104018545/image_104018545.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stock exchange crash\" data-id=\"104018545\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"2800px\" height=\"1980px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/104018545/image_104018545.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/104018545/image_104018545.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/104018545/image_104018545.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/104018545/image_104018545.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/104018545/image_104018545.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/104018545/image_104018545.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/104018545/image_104018545.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/104018545/image_104018545.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Edin</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>What Happened?</h2> <p>As I'm writing these lines, <strong>Novo Nordisk A/S</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVO\" title=\"Novo Nordisk A/S\">NVO</a>) is down about 16% on the pre-market session after the <a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/novo-next-generation-shot-helps-patients-lose-23-of-weight\" rel=\"nofollow\">news came out</a> that its obesity drug \u2014 CagriSema \u2014 delivered disappointing trial results, as Bloomberg reported an hour</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/104018545/image_104018545.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745572-novo-nordisk-a-rare-buying-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 17:15:17", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745566", "title": "7 Upcoming Dividend Increases", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Growth graph made of taller and taller gifts with last pillar being a Christmas tree\" data-id=\"2177999675\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"878px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>There are only a few days left until the Christmas holiday. While many of us are running around getting last-minute gifts, the companies on this list are giving investors an early present in higher dividends! I'm featuring</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177999675/image_2177999675.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745566-7-upcoming-dividend-increases", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 17:10:16", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745563", "title": "Ford: Don't Fall For This Dividend Play", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398845506/image_1398845506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Ford brand logo\" data-id=\"1398845506\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398845506/image_1398845506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398845506/image_1398845506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398845506/image_1398845506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398845506/image_1398845506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398845506/image_1398845506.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398845506/image_1398845506.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398845506/image_1398845506.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398845506/image_1398845506.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Vera Tikhonova</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Ford\u2019s (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/F\" title=\"Ford Motor Company\">F</a></span>) 6.2% dividend yield has been the focus of income investors looking for good yield in a market that has become quite expensive according to several metrics. Ford\u2019s dividend yield is significantly higher than the mere 1.2% yield</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398845506/image_1398845506.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745563-ford-dont-fall-for-this-dividend-play", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 17:02:20", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4744637", "title": "How I Would Retire Early With $1 Million Today", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"1 Million Celebration Balloons with Confetti\" data-id=\"1401505902\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">asbe</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Co-produced by Austin Rogers</em></p> <p>At some point in one's career, it is natural to wonder, \"What am I working toward?\"</p> <p>For a select few, the enjoyment of the work is an end-goal in itself. For those folks, their career is their</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4744637-how-i-would-retire-early-with-1-million-today", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 17:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745582", "title": "Reitmans (Canada) Limited 2025 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Reitmans (Canada) Limited in conjunction with their 2025 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106266\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745582-reitmans-canada-limited-2025-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 16:54:56", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745449", "title": "My Highest Conviction REIT Investment Idea: Big Yellow Group", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Golden egg in egg cup\" data-id=\"130409767\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1151px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/130409767/image_130409767.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekinga